          <li>Click the extension icon in your browser toolbar</li>
          <li>You'll be redirected to connect your account</li>
          <li>Once connected, you're ready to go!</li>
        </ol>

        <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)]">How to Use</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Navigate to any article or blog post you want to listen to</li>
