        </p>
        <ol class="mt-4 list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Right-click</strong> the extension icon</li>
          <li>Select <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Disconnect from TTS</strong></li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mt-4">
          You can also disconnect from your <%= link_to "account settings", settings_extensions_path, class: "text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" %>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)]">Troubleshooting</h2>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">"This page does not appear to be an article"</h3>
        <p class="mt-2">
          The extension works best on article pages with substantial text content. It may not work on:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Home pages or index pages</li>
          <li>Pages with mostly images or video</li>
          <li>Pages behind paywalls or login walls</li>
          <li>PDFs or non-HTML content</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Extension shows error state</h3>
        <p class="mt-2">
